{"analytics_identifier":"OT1294","base_path":"/government/organisations/united-kingdom-security-vetting","content_id":"471796ac-7421-4425-9cc6-a27ad81e850a","description":"United Kingdom Security Vetting (UKSV) is the single government provider of National Security Vetting (NSV). We are the centre of excellence for security vetting and enable government to protect citizens and provide vital public services, by understanding and managing personnel security risks. UKSV is part of the Cabinet Office .","details":{"acronym":"UKSV","alternative_format_contact_email":"uksv-helpdesk@cabinetoffice.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>United Kingdom Security Vetting (UKSV) is the single government provider of National Security Vetting (NSV). We are the centre of excellence for security vetting and enable government to protect citizens and provide vital public services, by understanding and managing personnel security risks.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"United Kingdom Security Vetting\">UKSV</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/cabinet-office\">Cabinet Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"cabinet-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"United Kingdom<br/>Security Vetting"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Detailed guide","href":"/guidance/united-kingdom-security-vetting-contact-us","image":{"alt_text":"graphic representing question and answer","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/63934ce28fa8f546d6bce59d/s712_RESIZED_FOR_GOV.UK_GettyImages-_enquiry_icon.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/63934ce3d3bf7f1a6940e32f/s465_RESIZED_FOR_GOV.UK_GettyImages-_enquiry_icon.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/63934ce2d3bf7f1a630283cd/RESIZED_FOR_GOV.UK_GettyImages-_enquiry_icon.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-05T09:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=